{"tid":1916054,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE SANA-MOMO擔任JYP日本女團選秀《Nizi Project》客座評委！","createTime":"2020-03-08T15:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T11:33:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c676802cd93c6afa7d7f7271558a97ff5cbac8a8","tid":1916054,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"JYP和Sony Music聯手製作的選秀節目《Nizi Project》從去年7~8月開始在日本的8座城市以及LA、夏威夷，選拔2020年出道的JYP日本女團成員，朴軫永擔任評委。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該節目從1月31日起每週五播出，目前播出至第1季第7集明星特質考核環節。除了在日本平臺播出，為了回應呼聲，JYP官方YouTube從3月6日起公開完整版。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EeuwKvHjXMA&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEeuwKvHjXMA%26feature%3Demb_title&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caMyUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=8101aebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EeuwKvHjXMA&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n經過初選和複賽之後，在第三輪接受朴軫永評審。從1萬名報名者中突圍最終入選的26人在東京合宿五天四夜。合宿期間依次對舞蹈、歌唱、明星特質、人品進行四輪考核。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wgmC27Aj7O0&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwgmC27Aj7O0%26feature%3Demb_title&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caMyUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=d1c888ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wgmC27Aj7O0&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Um2nvpUrVYk&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUm2nvpUrVYk%26feature%3Demb_title&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caMyUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=5df48e2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Um2nvpUrVYk&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\nSANA和MOMO將在組隊（人品）考核環節登場，讓參賽者們震驚。不知道SAMO有沒有私心pick哪個人呢？<br />\n<br />\n第1季是各地選拔的過程和26人合宿考核的內容，第2季展示晉級者在韓國的半年合宿訓練，以及最終評審和女團誕生瞬間。一起見證JYP日本女團的誕生吧！<br />\n<br />\n圖：Twitter"